descriptionHTML:
TGram Wear is a messaging App that let you send messages using voice commands or text inputs to your contacts using Telegram's code

This isn't a official Telegram app.

TGram Wear, uses the official Telegram code with some modifications that prepare a list of users to use on your Android Wear so you can watch your contact list and send voice and text messages to your Telegram contacts.
